cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL. 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the task of lane detection for autonomous driving. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a deep learning approach, which suggests that it could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of a segmentation-like weight map, which could potentially fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
